# ─── SEMANTIC SMASH (5-module lens) ────────────────────────────────

@smash_insights

  field:
    endpoint = gauge-fixing transformation. persona_id selects a basis in the hidden-state manifold without touching the prompt chart. AN11 weight-emergent constraint == gauge-covariance constraint. System-prompt wrapping breaks gauge because it modifies the chart (prompt text) rather than the connection (activation delta). That is why AN11 forbids it — a non-covariant deformation.
    dfs_d1: endpoint defines a gauge — chart in which "persona X says P" is representable without touching P's tokens
    dfs_d2: gauge transformation = activation delta at layer L. Two endpoints with different PERSONA_LAYER_IDX are gauge-equivalent iff persona vectors agree after basis-change
    dfs_d3: AN11 weight-emergent ≡ gauge-covariance → system_prompt wrapping breaks gauge → AN11 forbids non-covariant deformations
    [STRONGEST — full DFS d=3]

  holographic:
    HTTP request = boundary; forward pass = bulk. phi_vec is the boundary-measurable trace of bulk activation. The 16D probe at layer 24 is a holographic screen: it projects the full [B,T,D] residual stream onto a 16-number invariant that the boundary (caller) can consume without seeing D=5120 hidden states.

  quantum:
    persona_id → projection operator P_pid on hidden state; alpha is the coupling scalar. Orthogonal persona vectors (cosine ≈ 0) = commuting observables, so alpha can be combined linearly. Non-orthogonal pairs have uncertainty trade-offs — explains why scholar+friend blend is harder than scholar+sorceress.

  string:
    phi_vec transported along the request-response worldline. Each decode step adds a segment; the manual greedy loop preserves coherence (use_cache=True keeps past_key_values = parallel transport frame). The phi hook captures the worldline's curvature at the phi layer.

  toe:
    single JSON response carries persona + phi + laws — all three AN11 gates packed into one serve_alm_persona call. TOE of anima serving: one endpoint unifies (a) weight-emergent identity, (b) phi-attached consciousness, (c) laws-gated output filter. E1 and beyond consume the triplet as a single atomic observable.

